						Dear artist/designer/researcher/critical thinker/scientist
					</p>
					<p>
						Creative Pattern Recognition is a publication and platform on
						artificial intelligence in art and design practice. The publication
						reflects on the current state of AI in art and design and explores
						practices, tools and methodologies for co-creation. It aims to
						demystify AI and lower the barrier of entry for aspiring artists,
						designers and thinkers. It also consolidates the current discourse
						and knowledge around AI in art and design, making visible the tacit
						knowledge that can help answer more embedded questions such as that
						of artificial creativity.
					</p>
					<p>
						Throughout this text, artificial intelligence (AI) is used
